arts.ttl: Digie own goal sees Leyton Orient beat Tamworth
arts.sum: League One Leyton Orient progress to the second round of the FA Cup after beating National League Tamworth 1-0, thanks to Kennedy Digie's own goal.

arts.ttl: FA Cup draw live: Non-league minnows to learn second round opponents
arts.sum: The FA Cup draw, which precedes Tamworth v Leyton Orient, will serve up the second round ties, which will feature Carlisle and Gateshead after first round shocks at the weekend
